[1]Nĩ gĩkeno kĩnene gĩa kuonana na inyuĩ,Tũtũmĩtwo nĩ Ngai tũke tũhunjĩrie.Kĩrĩndi gĩa gũkũ thĩ nĩakĩendete mũno,Nĩ endaga kĩhonoke gĩtuĩke kĩa rũru rũake.[2]Thikĩrĩriai inyuothe mũigue ũhoro mwega,Nanĩ wakũmũkenia mũikare na thayũ.Jesu kristo nĩokire kũhonokia ehia,Onawe ũrĩ ũmwe wao itĩkia ũmũthĩ.[3]Mũthenya wa ithirĩro tũngĩkorwo ithuothe,Tũrĩ a Mwathani ũmwe Mwathani witũ Ngai.Nĩgũkagĩa gĩkeno gĩkeno kĩnene,Ithe nyina na ciana makĩinuka mũciĩ ũmwe.
